# Model Checkpoints

Trained model weights are hosted externally due to GitHub's file-size
limits (largest checkpoint, the fine-tuned RoBERTa-large encoder, is
~1.4 GB).

**Download from Hugging Face Hub:**
```bash
pip install huggingface_hub
python -c "
from huggingface_hub import snapshot_download
snapshot_download(repo_id='remyasree/meia-hmf-ecrl-v1',
                   local_dir='checkpoints/')
"
```

## Released Checkpoints

| File | Component | Size | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `mpm_text_encoder.bin` | MPM (text) | ~1.4 GB | RoBERTa-large fine-tuned 10 epochs on MetaConvo-50K |
| `mpm_vision_encoder.bin` | MPM (vision) | ~350 MB | ViT-B/16 fine-tuned on Stage 1 |
| `mpm_gesture_encoder.pt` | MPM (gesture) | ~12 MB | TCN fine-tuned on MetaGesture-30K |
| `mpm_haptic_encoder.pt` | MPM (haptic) | ~3 MB | 1D-CNN trained from scratch |
| `cafl_bse_stage2.pt` | CAFL + BSE | ~45 MB | Joint Stage 2 pretraining checkpoint |
| `ecrl_policy_seed{0-4}.pt` | ECRL policy | ~28 MB each | Final policy, one per seed (Figure 2) |
| `demographic_inference_head.pt` | Section 4.3 | ~2 MB | Balanced accuracy 0.78 (Supplementary D) |

All checkpoints are released under CC BY 4.0 (see `data/LICENSE_DATA.md`).
